# 🔐 SSH Setup & Git Workflow – Velvet Lab

## 🔑 SSH Setup

### Cek SSH Key
```bash
ls ~/.ssh
````

### Generate SSH Key (jika belum ada)

```bash
ssh-keygen -t ed25519 -C "email_kamu@example.com"
```

### Jalankan SSH Agent

```bash
eval "$(ssh-agent -s)"
```

### Tambahkan SSH Key

```bash
ssh-add ~/.ssh/id_ed25519
```

### Copy Public Key

```bash
cat ~/.ssh/id_ed25519.pub
```

### Tambahkan ke GitHub

1. Buka GitHub
2. Masuk ke **Settings → SSH and GPG keys**
3. Klik **New SSH Key**
4. Paste key yang sudah di-copy

### Tes Koneksi

```bash
ssh -T git@github.com
```

Jika berhasil:

```
Hi username! You've successfully authenticated...
```

---

### Ganti Remote ke SSH

```bash
cd velvet-lab
git remote set-url origin git@github.com:username/velvet-lab.git
git remote -v
```

---

# 🌿 Git Workflow

## 🌱 Mulai Kerja (Gunakan Branch Baru)

> ❗ Jangan langsung bekerja di `main` / `master`

```bash
git checkout -b coffee-shop-tui
git add .
git commit -m "add: initial README for velvet lab"
git push origin coffee-shop-tui
```

---

## 🔀 Merge ke Main / Master

### ✅ Cara Aman (Recommended - via GitHub)

1. Buka repository di GitHub
2. Buat Pull Request (PR)
3. Review & Merge

---

### ⚡ Cara Cepat (Local)

```bash
git checkout main
git pull origin main
git merge coffee-shop-tui
git push origin mainx
```

---

## 🧹 Clean Up Branch

```bash
git branch -d coffee-shop-tui
git push origin --delete coffee-shop-tui
```

---

## 📝 Format Commit

* `add:` init atau tambah file baru
* `del:` hapus fitur
* `feat:` fitur baru
* `fix:` bug fix
* `docs:` dokumentasi
* `refactor:` refaktor kode (improvement)
* `test:` unit testing
* `chore:` lainnya

